The paper proposes a method for end-to-end autonomous driving using deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and machine learning (cs.LG). The method also involves generating semantic birdeye masks, which relates to computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper deals with control and decision-making in autonomous driving, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
